sourceMeaningMnemonic: Give <radical>trash</radical> to the <radical>moon</radical> and it will <kanji>nurture</kanji> and <kanji>raise</kanji> that trash like it's its own little moon baby.
meaningInfo: Picture the moon raising this ball of trash, giving it love and attention.
readingMnemonic: The moon <kanji>nurture</kanji>s the trash ball until one day, it speaks! "<reading><ja>行く</ja></reading> (<ja>いく</ja>), <ja>行く！</ja>" it says. It wants to go live with mom moon!
readingInfo: Watch as the little trash ball <ja>行く</ja>s up into the sky and floats around its moon mama. If you raise your child right it will want to <ja>行く</ja> wherever you go too.
